data.description: This two story house is a rare find in Hialeah. It has been recently updated featuring four bedrooms with a very large Master suite on the main floor that offer endless possibilities. Laundry inside the house and as a plus a very large storage house in the back. Large driveway. perfect for a big family. Potential income opportunity. This property has a lot to offer, come by and look no further. Wont last. Room for potential for in-laws quarters.
